text: Bryan Murphy (born 1993) is an Irish hurler. Bryan Murphy may also refer to: *Bryan Murphy (Gaelic footballer) (born 1967), Irish Gaelic football manager and dual player of hurling and Gaelic football *Bryan Murphy (athlete) represented Ireland at the 2006 European Athletics Championships *Bryan Murphy (American football), played in 2008 Boston College Eagles football team ==See also== *Brian Murphy (disambiguation)
